            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間25日12:37，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲12.54點（或4.01%），暫報325.28點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-2.58%</li><li>近 1 月：+0.42%</li><li>近 3 月：+15.94%</li><li>近 6 月：+18.07%</li><li>今年以來：+13.21%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>SDN概念領漲+7.64%。其中    華星光(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4979:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4979\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4979-TW</a>)            上漲        9.95%            ;        眾達-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4977:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4977\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4977-TW</a>)            上漲        9.92%            ;        智邦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2345:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2345\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2345-TW</a>)            上漲        9.77%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>無線網路概念領漲+6.71%。其中    智邦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2345:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2345\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2345-TW</a>)            上漲        9.77%            ;        昇陽半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8028:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href